@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.23 + (wp.abs(v1 + 0.58) * v1))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 1.00) / (v0 + 0.40 * v1 + 0.01)) * 0.21)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.96))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(0.97))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.17) - 0.85))
    v0 = (0.36 + wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.53)))
    data[tid] = v0
